data.description: Your dream home is waiting for you in Murfreesboro! This charming 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom with 2 car garage home is now on the market! The kitchen boasts generous marbled granite counter space, stainless appliances and beautiful light cabinetry that compliments the tile backsplash, making cooking and entertaining a delight. Flow into the living space, complete with cozy fireplace and vaulted ceilings, perfect for curling up on the couch with a good book! Discover a bright interior with neutral laminate flooring throughout the home as well as accented features like ceiling fans and wood blinds in each room. The main bedroom boasts a private ensuite bathroom with a large closet. Relax with your favorite drink in the fenced in backyard on the wood deck and plan your next family event to host.
